So what is the plan for critical role now? Are they just going to continue with one shots or is there a new campaign that is going to happen? (Just finished the last episode)

Critical Role will continue airing on Thursdays at the regular time. There will be one-shots and other fun things until the end of the year, and then in January a new campaign will begin, set 20 years after the story of Vox Machina. Don't worry, Critters, the show isn't going anywhere. ❤
